{"tid":707754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡77歲老婦Skype識可疑男 4年被騙200萬元","createTime":"2018-06-19T00:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T01:08:50.000Z","uid":122,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e0c2be79d230ff84515bff046acce2ae0abdf2fe","tid":707754,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:23:10.000Z","msg":"一名77歲姓黃老婦，4年前透過社交媒體Skype認識一名男子，其後男子將一個聲稱裝有財物的行李箱交由老婦保管，並多次以不同理由，要求她存款至一個指定戶口，於是多年來多次存款，合共存入約200萬元。<br />\n<br />\n老婦其後發現行李箱內是一些廢紙。其46歲女兒昨日得悉事件，懷疑母親受騙，於是在紅磡紅磡邨紅曜樓單位內報案。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報經初步調查，案件暫列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進，暫時未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"a44cbc541bb87a31205d27bbf362d15dfbc99663","tid":707754,"uid":10998,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:28:09.000Z","msg":"香港人真係有好多錢俾人呃"},{"pid":"3edee845195cfeb1a4154052c987a6f40a6b318d","tid":707754,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:28:21.000Z","msg":"77<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c5cf06233782e4d628ebc8bb759e90b7658ca8","tid":707754,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:31:06.000Z","msg":"77歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221903ce29b48829b80ac701f997913916fbbe3e","tid":707754,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:35:01.000Z","msg":"有無牛油帶過嚟呀"},{"pid":"b29b2069c8ab0c8e995fa9252b60ef6c3771f7a2","tid":707754,"uid":59602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a44cbc541bb87a31205d27bbf362d15dfbc99663","tid":707754,"uid":10998,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:28:09.000Z","msg":"香港人真係有好多錢俾人呃"},"citedBy":0,"rep